Here’s a glimpse of Lakmē Sun Expert x Saaksha & Kinni present The Sunstopper Party at Lakmē Fashion Week in partnership with FDCI.

Saaksha & Kinni’s collection draws inspiration from Gujarat’s Adalaj Stepwell, incorporating its floral motifs and geometric patterns into bold prints. The duo blends feminine fabrics with strong silhouettes, featuring hand micro-pleating, layering, and statement-making designs.

Lightweight chiffons, cottons, and satins keep the collection summer-ready, with lycra swimwear and canvas jackets adding an edgy touch. The color palette reflects the stepwell’s essence—sunlit oranges and browns, watery blues, and vibrant reds and purples inspired by local Gujarati women.

With flowy dresses, kaftans, and breezy jackets, the collection offers a chic, elevated holiday wardrobe that celebrates joy, ease, and the spirit of Lakme Fashion Week in partnership with FDCI’s 25th year.

☀️ Heard the term photostability in sunscreens? Let’s decode it.
Photostability = your sunscreen’s ability to stay effective even after sun exposure.
If a formula breaks down under UV rays, it stops protecting your skin!
That’s why it matters.

✨ The good news? Lakmē sunscreens use photostable UV filters.
So your protection doesn’t quit when the sun comes out.

Give skin what it needs and nothing else! The concept of listening to your skin may sometimes get overcomplicated. Here is the thing—listening to your skin and giving it what it needs is really about being aware of your skin behaviors. 
 
Tightness, excessive oiliness, dryness/flaking, congestion, irritation—these are all behaviors that are signals sent by your skin in response to factors such as environment, the products you’re using, or changes in your personal health.

To reset skin to its happiest, healthiest state, we recommend taking a #drunkbreak. 

During a #drunkbreak, we avoid the #suspicious6 (essential oils, drying alcohols, silicones, chemical sunscreens, fragrances/ dyes, and SLS). These are six categories of ingredients, which, research has shown, can be at the root of common skin issues, such as sensitivity and breakouts.

The Sleep-Hormone Cycle: A Vicious Loop

Hormonal imbalances can lead to poor sleep quality, and poor sleep, in turn, can exacerbate hormone dysregulation. Supporting your body with plant-powered solutions like Juna’s Nightcap Sleep Gummies can help restore hormonal balance, improve sleep quality, and enhance overall wellness. Why Are We So Tired?

Women face unique challenges when it comes to sleep—hormonal shifts, mental load, caregiving roles, and life stages all play a part. Here’s what the data says:

💤 1 in 3 women get less than the recommended 7 hours of sleep per night (CDC).
💤 47% of working moms report poor sleep quality due to stress and balancing multiple roles.
💤 Women are 40% more likely than men to experience insomnia symptoms.
💤 75-84% of pregnant women deal with disrupted sleep due to physical discomfort, hormonal changes, and anxiety.
💤 Women are 2x more likely than men to experience anxiety and depression, both linked to poor sleep.
💤 Nearly 50% of postmenopausal women struggle with sleep due to hormonal shifts.
💤 46% of women over 50 report frequent sleep problems related to aging, stress, and health conditions.
💤 Women are 1.3x more likely than men to wake up feeling tired, even after a full night’s sleep.
💤 A third of women report disrupted sleep during their menstrual cycle, especially in the luteal phase.

We sleep a third of our lives, yet so many of us struggle to get the rest we need. What’s been your biggest challenge when it comes to sleep?

In 2023, Catch Spices launched its #MaakaEhsaas campaign for Mother’s Day, featuring a heartfelt film about a mother who distanced herself from her daughter to protect her from life’s hardships. Despite the separation, she cooked and secretly delivered food to her daughter at an orphanage, using food as their emotional connection. Created by Grapes and The Titus Upputuru Company, the campaign reinforced Catch’s message that food is more than just food-it’s a powerful expression of a mother’s love.

Agency: Grapes Worldwide ( @grapes_worldwide )
Brand: Catch Foods ( @catch_foods )
Director: Titus Upputuru ( @titusupputuru )
Production House: The Titus Upputuru Company ( @thetitusupputurucompany )

#CampaignThrowback #SSMothersDayWatch
Mood swings, sponsored by appraisal season🤯

Back in 2024, Brazilian beauty brand O Boticário marked Mother’s Day with a moving short film called Tempest that captured the emotional storms between mothers and teenagers. 

Created by AlmapBBDO, the four-minute film leaned into realism and metaphor, showing a literal storm to mirror family tensions and eventual healing. It stood out for its cinematic flair, sustainability efforts, and emotional depth. Backed by a Harvard study showing similar anxiety and depression rates in both groups, the campaign shed light on the often-overlooked struggles of parenting adolescents.

Agency: AlmapBBDO ( @almapbbdo )
Brand: O Boticário ( @oboticario )

Swipe ⬅️ Italian artist Salvatore Garau sold an invisible sculpture titled “Io Sono” (“I Am”) for over $18,000 through the Art-Rite auction house. 💰🤯

The buyer received only a certificate of authenticity — the piece itself is immaterial. Garau insists the sculpture exists as “air and spirit” within a 5-by-5-foot space and is meant to stimulate the imagination. “You don’t see it but it exists,” the artist said, defending the work as a conceptual exploration of energy and presence.

This is not Garau’s first foray into unseen art — earlier works include “Buddha In Contemplation” and “Afrodite Piange”.

How much would y’all pay for this!? 🤔🤣

Fyr op under julen med denne krydrede linsesuppe 🥣🌱🍑
Vinteren kalder på varme og smag, og vores krydrede linsesuppe med abrikos leverer på begge dele. Suppen fungerer som en mættende hovedret fyldt med protein fra linserne, og kan også serveres med groft brød eller en rest ris for ekstra fylde. 🌟

💚 Opskrift til 4 serveringer:
Ingredienser:
2 spsk Urtekram kokosolie
4 fed hvidløg
1 rødløg
6 Urtekram tørrede abrikoser
1 spsk revet frisk ingefær
2 tsk Urtekram karry
1 tsk Urtekram stødt gurkemeje
1 tsk Urtekram kardemomme
1 courgette i skiver
2 dåser Urtekram kokosmælk
3 dl vand
3 dl Urtekram røde linser
2 tsk havsalt
70 g babyspinat

Pynt:
Friske korianderblade

Fremgangsmåde:
1. Varm kokosolie i en stor gryde.
2. Skær rødløget i skiver og hak hvidløg og abrikoser.
3. Steg løg, hvidløg og abrikoser i olien sammen med revet ingefær, karry, gurkemeje og kardemomme.
4. Tilsæt courgette og steg, indtil den er blød.
5. Tilsæt kokosmælk, vand, linser og salt. Lad suppen småkoge i 20-25 minutter.
6. Sluk for varmen og rør spinat i.
7. Server suppen i skåle og top med friske korianderblade.

Velbekomme og glædelig jul!

Del gerne dine erfaringer med os 💚

🎄 December uden risengrød? Som et juletræ uden pynt! Tjek – kaneldrysset er på plads. Fordi ingen december er komplet uden en skefuld jul på tallerkenen.🎅✨Vores ingredienser tager din julegrød til næste niveau.

Olie-essentials til dit køkken - Urtekram har alt, hvad du overhovedet har brug for af olie! 💚 

Og husk, at der er plads til variation - brug gerne flere forskellige olier i din madlavning for at skabe endnu mere dybde i smagen.

Bønner, bønner, bønner! 

Vores chilibønner bringer en rig, jordisk smag til en kraftig chili. Tacobønner tilføjer et stænk af krydderi til dine tex-mex-favoritter og vores blandede bønner tilbyder en vidunderlig variation af teksturer og næringsstoffer.

Pakket med protein, fiber og essentielle vitaminer er bønner et bæredygtigt og overkommelig basisfoder. Så fyld op på disse lækre bønnesorter - både din smagsløg og planeten vil takke dig! 🌎

At lave god hverdagsmad behøver ikke at være kompliceret!

One pan pasta, 2 personer:

200 g spaghetti
125 g feta
1 rødløg
2 fed hvidløg, revet
250 g cherrytomater
50 g oliven, uden sten
3 dl vand
4 spsk olivenolie
2 tsk Italian Spice Mix
havsalt og friskkværnet sort peber
frisk basilikum

Tænd ovnen på 180 grader, varmluft. Smør et stort ildfast fad med en smule olie. Læg spaghetti i fadet - og top med feta i et helt stykke, hakket løg, hvidløg, halve tomater og oliven. Hæld vand henover, og top med olivenolie, Italian Spice Mix og krydr gavmildt med havsalt og peber. 

Bag fadet i ovnen i cirka 25 minutter - tjek efter 15 minutter, for at tjekke om der skal hældes mere vand i fadet og smag evt på pastaen. Tag fadet ud af ovnen og vend forsigtigt det hele godt rundt. Top med frisk basilikum og et drys af Italian Spice Mix . 

Hvis du gerne vil gøre måltidet mere proteinrigt, så kan du servere fisk til retten, fx et stykke varmrøget laks eller et stykke bagt, hvid fisk.

Æble (pandekage) sæson! 🍎

Nu begynder æblerne at hænge tungt i træerne, og det betyder, at det er tid til morgenmadspandekager. Vores bedste æblepandekager får deres luftige konsistens, fordi de er lavet med æblemos i stedet for banan. 
*1 dl Urtekram økologiske mandelmel
*1 dl usødet æblemos
*1 dl havremælk 
*1 dl havregryn 
*1/2 tsk bagepulver
*1/2 tsk kanel
*En knivspids salt
*2 æg
Mørtel havregryn i mel eller kør dem i en blender. Pisk alle ingredienserne sammen. Hæld en teskefuld kokosolie i en medium varm stegepande og klik små tykke pandekager ud. Det er cirka 15 minipandekager pr. Dej.

Vidste du, at økologisk mad gør en forskel for kroppen?
Ved at spise økologisk reducerer du dit kemiske indtag kraftigt, da økologisk landbrug ikke bruger kemikalier i dyrkningen. Undersøgelser har vist, at økologiske fødevarer indeholder højere niveauer af antioxidanter. Vælg økologi og gør en forskel for miljøet og verden!

What makes C-Luma different from C-Firma? C for yourself!

Think of C-Luma as C-Firma’s gentler cousin. C-Luma contains two milder, less acidic forms of vitamin C at a lower strength (10.0%). The formula includes hydration-boosting ingredients and has a unique, lightweight water-serum texture. If C-Firma is too strong for you, you may enjoy C-Luma.

Like C-Firma, C-Luma will help improve hyperpigmentation and signs of aging, just at a more gradual pace, while also addressing unique skin concerns like redness and breakouts. C-Luma can be used alongside any of our actives and even used twice daily (morning and night!). 

You can alternate them, too! Try using C-Firma in the morning and C-Luma at night for even greater results.

A Mother’s Day Message from Lisa, Founder of Up North Naturals. 

Hello, beautiful community,

As Mother’s Day approaches, I’m reflecting on the different experiences that accompany this special day. 

Each year, I share the “Thinking of You” image that recognizes the diverse emotions surrounding this day: those who have lost their mothers, those navigating strained relationships, those who chose not to be moms, and those who long to be mothers.

Personally, my journey to motherhood was one of longing and patience. After more than 15 years of marriage, my husband and I made the life-changing decision to adopt our son. It was the best decision we ever made, filling our lives with more joy and a feeling of being complete.

This year, we also carry the weight of loss, having recently said goodbye to a cherished woman in our lives—my mother-in-law. Her absence is deeply felt, especially by my husband. I’m holding him close in my thoughts today.

To all who are incredible caregivers and nurturers, yet have chosen not to have children, your love and compassion enrich the lives of those around you. Thank you for embracing and caring for others’ children with open arms. Today, I am thinking of you too.

Remember, relationships can be complex and sometimes strained. This can hurt deeply, especially when it involves our own children or parents. Mother’s Day can amplify these feelings, but know that you are not alone in this.

To all the wonderful mothers out there, Including my own mom, sisters, and nieces, I encourage you to spend this day as you wish. Whether it’s taking time for yourself or celebrating with loved ones, honor what feels right for you.

Let’s remember to be compassionate and supportive to one another, acknowledging that Mother’s Day can be a tender time for many.

Sending love to each of you,
🥰 Lisa

Få mere smag i hverdagen! Urtekrams krydderier giver masser af smag og er altid økologiske. Vælg øko. Vælg Urtekram. 💚

Hvilken af vores krydderier er din favorit?

Har du lyst til at udforske de lækre og fyldige smagsnoter fra Asien? Prøv at give din wok et skud! Med blot få ingredienser som tamari, frisk ingefær og kokosmælk kan du skabe retter, der eksploderer af smagsfylde.

Skal din januar være lettere? Prøv vores salat med græskar og æble 🍂🥗🍏 

Bliv dejlig mæt med denne lækre salat med græskar og æble – en mættende hovedret fyldt med proteinrige bønner, der gør den til et perfekt måltid🌟

💚 Opskrift til 4 serveringer:
Ingredienser:
½ hokkaido græskar (ca. 500 g)
3 spsk Urtekram ekstra jomfru olivenolie
2 tsk havsalt
1 tsk Urtekram spidskommen
½ tsk Urtekram cayennepeber
100 g grønkål
1 dåse Urtekram butter beans
1 rødt æble i skiver
1/2 dl Urtekram tørrede tranebær
75 g feta i mindre stykker
25 g hakkede salte Urtekram mandler

Dressing:
2 spsk Urtekram ekstra jomfru olivenolie
1 spsk Urtekram æblecidereddike
1 spsk Urtekram agavesirup
½ tsk havsalt

Fremgangsmåde:
1. Skær græskarret i mundrette stykker (lad skrællen sidde på).
2. Rør olie, salt, spidskommen og cayennepeber sammen i en skål og vend græskarstykkerne heri.
3. Fordel græskarstykker på en plade med bagepapir og bag dem i 20-25 min. ved 225 grader.
4. Rør olie, eddike, sirup og salt sammen til en dressing.
5. Riv bladene af grønkålsstokken, hak dem groft og læg dem på et stort serveringsfad.
6. Hæld dressingen over. Kram kålen godt med dressingen til kålen bliver blød og falder lidt sammen.
7. Fordel de bagte græskarstykker, butter beans, æbler, tranebær, feta og mandler på salaten og server.

Tip:
Det kan anbefales at kramme kålen med fx dressing, fetaost eller bare lidt salt. Det får kålen til at smide væske, så den bliver mere sprød, og samtidig rundere og mildere i smagen. 

Del gerne dine erfaringer med os 💚

Tyvstart det nye år med en ovnristet luksusmysli 🥣🌱

Start dagen med en sprød og økologisk oplevelse. Prøv vores ovnristede luksusmysli, perfekt som mættende topping på græsk yoghurt, skyr eller chiagrød. Top med sæsonens friske eller tørrede frugter og bær – en sund og lækker morgenmadsfavorit! 🌟

Ingredienser:
400 g Urtekram flager, fx havregryn, spelt- og rugflager
50 g Urtekram boghvedegryn
100 g Urtekram mandler eller andre nødder
50 g Urtekram sesamfrø
50 g Urtekram ristede kokoschips
Et nip salt
1,5 dl Urtekram ahornsirup
1 dl Urtekram kokosolie
75 g Urtekram tørret frugt, f.eks. tranebær og gojibær

Fremgangsmåde:
1. Forvarm ovnen til 180 grader.
2. Bland gryn, flager, nødder, frø, kokoschips og salt på en plade med bagepapir.
3. Dryp sirup og kokosolie over blandingen, sæt pladen i ovnen og bag den i 5 min.
4. Vend myslien rundt i den smeltede olie og sirup.
5. Bag i yderligere 20-25 min., og vend rundt undervejs.
6. Tag myslien ud af ovnen og lad den køle af. Vend den tørrede frugt heri.
7. Opbevar myslien i en tætsluttende beholder.

Del gerne din morgenmadsinspiration med os 💚

Fyr op under julen med denne krydrede linsesuppe 🥣🌱🍑
Vinteren kalder på varme og smag, og vores krydrede linsesuppe med abrikos leverer på begge dele. Suppen fungerer som en mættende hovedret fyldt med protein fra linserne, og kan også serveres med groft brød eller en rest ris for ekstra fylde. 🌟

💚 Opskrift til 4 serveringer:
Ingredienser:
2 spsk Urtekram kokosolie
4 fed hvidløg
1 rødløg
6 Urtekram tørrede abrikoser
1 spsk revet frisk ingefær
2 tsk Urtekram karry
1 tsk Urtekram stødt gurkemeje
1 tsk Urtekram kardemomme
1 courgette i skiver
2 dåser Urtekram kokosmælk
3 dl vand
3 dl Urtekram røde linser
2 tsk havsalt
70 g babyspinat

Pynt:
Friske korianderblade

Fremgangsmåde:
1. Varm kokosolie i en stor gryde.
2. Skær rødløget i skiver og hak hvidløg og abrikoser.
3. Steg løg, hvidløg og abrikoser i olien sammen med revet ingefær, karry, gurkemeje og kardemomme.
4. Tilsæt courgette og steg, indtil den er blød.
5. Tilsæt kokosmælk, vand, linser og salt. Lad suppen småkoge i 20-25 minutter.
6. Sluk for varmen og rør spinat i.
7. Server suppen i skåle og top med friske korianderblade.

Velbekomme og glædelig jul!

Del gerne dine erfaringer med os 💚

🎄 December uden risengrød? Som et juletræ uden pynt! Tjek – kaneldrysset er på plads. Fordi ingen december er komplet uden en skefuld jul på tallerkenen.🎅✨Vores ingredienser tager din julegrød til næste niveau.

Olie-essentials til dit køkken - Urtekram har alt, hvad du overhovedet har brug for af olie! 💚 

Og husk, at der er plads til variation - brug gerne flere forskellige olier i din madlavning for at skabe endnu mere dybde i smagen.

At lave god hverdagsmad behøver ikke at være kompliceret!

One pan pasta, 2 personer:

200 g spaghetti
125 g feta
1 rødløg
2 fed hvidløg, revet
250 g cherrytomater
50 g oliven, uden sten
3 dl vand
4 spsk olivenolie
2 tsk Italian Spice Mix
havsalt og friskkværnet sort peber
frisk basilikum

Tænd ovnen på 180 grader, varmluft. Smør et stort ildfast fad med en smule olie. Læg spaghetti i fadet - og top med feta i et helt stykke, hakket løg, hvidløg, halve tomater og oliven. Hæld vand henover, og top med olivenolie, Italian Spice Mix og krydr gavmildt med havsalt og peber. 

Bag fadet i ovnen i cirka 25 minutter - tjek efter 15 minutter, for at tjekke om der skal hældes mere vand i fadet og smag evt på pastaen. Tag fadet ud af ovnen og vend forsigtigt det hele godt rundt. Top med frisk basilikum og et drys af Italian Spice Mix . 

Hvis du gerne vil gøre måltidet mere proteinrigt, så kan du servere fisk til retten, fx et stykke varmrøget laks eller et stykke bagt, hvid fisk.

Bønner, bønner, bønner! 

Vores chilibønner bringer en rig, jordisk smag til en kraftig chili. Tacobønner tilføjer et stænk af krydderi til dine tex-mex-favoritter og vores blandede bønner tilbyder en vidunderlig variation af teksturer og næringsstoffer.

Pakket med protein, fiber og essentielle vitaminer er bønner et bæredygtigt og overkommelig basisfoder. Så fyld op på disse lækre bønnesorter - både din smagsløg og planeten vil takke dig! 🌎

Æble (pandekage) sæson! 🍎

Nu begynder æblerne at hænge tungt i træerne, og det betyder, at det er tid til morgenmadspandekager. Vores bedste æblepandekager får deres luftige konsistens, fordi de er lavet med æblemos i stedet for banan. 
*1 dl Urtekram økologiske mandelmel
*1 dl usødet æblemos
*1 dl havremælk 
*1 dl havregryn 
*1/2 tsk bagepulver
*1/2 tsk kanel
*En knivspids salt
*2 æg
Mørtel havregryn i mel eller kør dem i en blender. Pisk alle ingredienserne sammen. Hæld en teskefuld kokosolie i en medium varm stegepande og klik små tykke pandekager ud. Det er cirka 15 minipandekager pr. Dej.

Vidste du, at økologisk mad gør en forskel for kroppen?
Ved at spise økologisk reducerer du dit kemiske indtag kraftigt, da økologisk landbrug ikke bruger kemikalier i dyrkningen. Undersøgelser har vist, at økologiske fødevarer indeholder højere niveauer af antioxidanter. Vælg økologi og gør en forskel for miljøet og verden!

Picture this: your dog is taking a nap, but you want to go pet or cuddle them. It’s hard to resist the urge, but we’re here to say: consider letting them be!

Those memories will stay with me forever. To say he was ahead of his time would be a big minimization. Whenever I was with Jonas, I felt stronger and unfuckwitable, he brought me ultimate confidence, strength and courage. There isn’t a single Asian in fashion today who could hold a candle to Jonas and what he meant to Asians all over the world(from industry insiders to those outside looking in.) He gave a lot of dudes in streetwear their birth in the business and nobody has a bad story about him. I just wish he could be here today so that my kids could have met him. We pushed each other to the maximum in everything and in 2006 we started using the term “to the moon” that’s no bullshit. Jonas, I miss you so much bro. Until the next life fam. You will always be loved by me. 💚💔 of course today’s episode of BTB is dedicated in honor of him. 🙏🏼

We kicked off the 2025 Harley Owners Group rally season with @justgkue deep in the heart of Southeast Texas, where coastal roads and Southern charm meet wide-open skies.

From G-Kue: “I’ve been a H.O.G. member for three years, but I had never attended a H.O.G. Rally. I went to Beaumont to check it out.

H.O.G. Rallies are centered around riding! The local chapters set pre-determined routes for you to go out and ride. Most of them are escorted rides, but you can go alone if you choose to. These rides are meant to show off the area, often going to or through cool places. I found myself on an Indian reservation and traveled to an old historic fort. Gas up before you go... the group will make stops, but make sure you’re on full prior to leaving.

You will be gone pretty much the entire day on these rides. Most start leaving about 10 a.m., and they’ll arrive back around 4–5 p.m.

Bring a camera... trust me.

It’s truly a family atmosphere. You gotta understand that some of these riders have been in H.O.G. for over 30 years. It’s easy to make friends, and next thing you know, you’re talking about the next one while reminiscing about the previous ones.

All in all, I had an awesome time! We rode all over... ate... laughed... took pictures... did I mention we rode? 🤣 Seriously, if you’re looking for an opportunity to get out and ride with some great people... consider joining your local H.O.G. chapter. I promise you won’t regret it. Peace ✌️”

#HarleyDavidson #HOG

Spring is well and truly here! 🌸 🐣 🌤️
But what does the Spring mean for our skin, and what do you need to be especially careful of when it comes to skincare?

Spring is the season when our skin is at its driest and most unstable. It has a weakened skin barrier function (winter has pushed it to its limits), so is less able to retain as much moisture and protect itself from the environment, including allergens like pollen. As the weather gets warmer and humidity levels increase, our skin has to learn to adapt yet again.

So what can we do to support our Spring skin? 🤔
By re-balancing the skin we can help it to retain moisture and build up its resilience to the changing climate and environment.

✨ Cleanse skin well, morning and night if you can
✨ Gently exfoliate once a week (our homemade scrub is perfectly gentle for this!)
✨ Moisturise more! Not just your face, but arms, legs and all the parts that have been hiding under a snuggly jumper 😉 
✨ Don’t forget your SPF! Choose one that protects agains UVA and B, and make sure you use it daily (even on cloudy days!) ⛅

Your skin produces more sebum in the warmer months, so you may find that your winter moisturiser feels a little too heavy. If so, consider choosing a lighter moisturiser that will reduce any skin-overload.
And most importantly, enjoy the sunshine and fresh air! ☺️ 💖

This Mother’s Day and Mental Health Awareness Month and I want to thank Mavi for being there for me in every moment- not just the happy ones. 

As many of you know I battle depression and while I am still learning to live with it, having Mavi in my life has really helped. 

It’s like an ocean… it goes out and it comes in. It can be all consuming and when it hits I am plagued with fatigue and emptiness. During that time nothing seems to shine. I’m very lucky that I always have Mavi by my side begging for a walk or willing to cuddle when I am a prisoner to my bed. Together we always get to the other side.
 
I partnered for #MentalHealthAwarenessMonth with @nulopetfood in support of the silent battle so many of us are fighting. Awareness is the first step, then from there it’s dissolving the stigma that surrounds mental health and keeps us hiding our private battles. If you are struggling- just know that you are not alone and there is always a light at the end of the tunnel.

Our Mission⁠
Focus On: The Encoreship⁠
⁠
Our why is female empowerment, and it is at the core of everything we do. Our key focus is on empowering women to be financially independent through employment. ⁠
⁠
Our mission is to empower women to have choices to help build a life full of passion and purpose, whatever that may be. We are firm believers that employment is the key to financial independence, and financial independence provides freedom of choice. Our belief in female support doesn’t stop at those already within our walls. We extend the offer through a pioneering employment program: The Encoreship. ⁠
⁠
Only 32% of mothers feel confident enough to re-enter the workforce (Get Qualified, 2016), and only 59% of mature age women (55 – 65 years) keep at it, compared to 72% of mature age men (Australian Government Women’s Workforce Participation, 2020). To us, that’s unacceptable, and highlights the undeniable inequalities prevalent in the workplace. With initiatives like The Encoreship, we can bridge that gap. ⁠
⁠
The Encoreship is a three-month paid placement for women facing challenges re-entering the corporate world (whatever that reason may be), with the sole purpose to help rebuild confidence, skills and support the transition back into the workforce, because everyone deserves to have a purpose-filled life. ⁠
⁠
In 2021, we welcomed our first inspiring and deserving woman into the program at DISSH, with 5 currently in our Encoreship Alumni. With a new year just getting started, we plan to do it all over again in 2025. ⁠
⁠
Sound like something you are interested in knowing more about? Reach out to PC@dissh.com.au and join our collective mission.⁠
⁠
Meet Lisa, our 2022 Encorer. ⁠

Our Mission
⁠
Don't get us a wrong, we're all about a (worldwide) day dedicated to women. That's our jam. But at DISSH, it's our mission to take inspired action to make real positive change to empower women and close the gap, every day.⁠
⁠
International Women's Day is a reminder of our why and an opportunity for us to highlight some pretty incredible initiatives to spread awareness and inspire action. We are working to make the women before us proud, and to help create an even playing field for the generations ahead. ⁠
⁠
This week we will be spotlighting valued partnerships across Thread Together and the Children's Hospital Foundation, and initiatives such as The Encoreship and Paid Parental Leave (and how your business can get involved) - all working towards the one overarching mission. ⁠
⁠
So, step away from the cupcakes (or grab one) and get a load of this.⁠
⁠
Focus on: The Mary McConnel Career Boost Program For Women In Paediatric Research⁠
⁠
We have pledged $450,000 over the next 3 years to support 3 inspiring female researchers annually in a bid to close the gender gap in academic research, and improve health outcomes for children.⁠
⁠
We sat down with one of the researchers, Dr. Anna Francis, to get to know more about her, celebrate the work she is doing and why closing the gap is so important.

In Focus: A close up of our latest campaign with creative partner and friend of the brand, @tigmitrading⁠
⁠
Founded in Byron Bay, Australia, by Danielle McEwan. Tigmi creates and curates a meticulous edit of iconic vintage furniture, art, and objects for your space.⁠
⁠
Danielle’s life-long love for culture and discerning eye for art and design in all forms, is what led her to launch Tigmi. Her only criteria when selecting each piece, is that it is made with love and inspires connection - adding an invisible, but palpable layer of beauty and soul to the home or space it’s in.⁠
⁠
A natural collaboration, pairing our DISSH refined yet laidback designs and very intentional aesthetic, with Tigmi’s unique perspective, seamlessly combining the beauty of aged vintage pieces with the elegance of modern design. My proudest mom moment.. 🙏
Indigo was having a bit of a hard time playing with other kids at the park. I told them, « it’s ok to be upset for as long as you want, and guess what when you’re ready, the quickest way to ground yourself back is to have a little meditation in the grass » First they ran around in the grass upset, and eventually, they went in the grass by themselves and did THIS 🧘🏻‍♀️… 😭😭😭😭 Then they came out of it and said « see, i feel better now » and they were soooo proud they did this by themselves !!!!!! 
It’s never too soon to teach kids about consciousness and how to self regulate their emotions ! LOOK !!!!!!! Magic !

I dont know who needs to hear this, but don’t be lying to your tuner… if you say, “nobody has touched it since you.” Then we read the tune file out of the ECU and the compare file looks like this… you just made your self look stupid for no reason lol

Another fine example of what E85 does to LT4’s and why the fuel system is the most important part of building them. Full Kong 2650 setup laid down 813 on 93 and 953 on E85. Which BTW was only at E67. Your ethanol content doesn’t matter. You just need like 60% or above to take advantage of the effects ethanol has, and you must have a fuel system that can support it. Go port or go home!

The difference between 93 and E85 on these things will never not impress me. 

The only ‘sort of’ difference between these 2 runs is that we put ice in the tank for the last run on E85, which net’d us about a 20 HP gain. 

So even if we were to compare iced to iced, we’re still talking over a 100 HP improvement from fuel quality alone. 

I blame GM’s piston design. People have their opinions, but this one is mine. The reason why I think it’s the pistons is because these cars run relatively fine on 93 with aftermarket pistons. I believe the sharp spots around the injector cups create hot spots which lead to detonation. 

I’m making a point of posting this because I find it to be more industry knowledge, than common knowledge, still with this platform…. And I honestly get tired of explaining why I suggest a 10k dollar fuel system anytime someone wants to upgrade their LT1/4’s to this power level and beyond. 😂😂

*And I’m not talking about upgrading the DI injectors or HPFP’s* which are ridiculously expensive and have a high failure/problem rate. 

It’s port injection for everything we do over here!
